<lb n="0560b09"/><head type="no">No. 746</head>
<lb n="0560b10"/><juan fun="open" n="001"><mulu type="卷" n="001"/><jhead><title>餓鬼報應<note n="0560011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">經＝出雜藏經【宋】【宮】，經＋（出雜藏經）夾註【元】【明】</note><app n="0560011"><lem>經</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【宮】" resp="Taisho">出雜藏經</rdg><rdg wit="【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">經<note place="inline">出雜藏經</note></rdg></app></title></jhead></juan>
<lb n="0560b11"/>
<lb n="0560b12"/><byline type="Translator">失<note n="0560012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">譯＋（人名）【明】</note><app n="0560012"><lem>譯</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">譯人名</rdg></app><note n="0560013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔附東晉錄〕－【宮】</note><app n="0560013"><lem>附東晉錄</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app></byline>
<lb n="0560b13"/><div1 type="jing"><p>尊者大目揵連。從佛在耆闍崛山<note n="0560014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔中〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0560014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔中〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0560014"><lem>中</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>。遊<note n="0560015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔行〕－【三】</note><note n="0560015" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔行〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0560015"><lem>行</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>
<lb n="0560b14"/><note n="0560016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔&M010527;〕－【宮】</note><app n="0560016"><lem>&M010527;</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>水邊。見諸餓鬼甚多。受罪不同。見尊者
<lb n="0560b15"/>目連。皆起敬心。來問因<note n="0560017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">緣＝由【三】【宮】</note><note n="0560017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">緣＝由【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0560017"><lem>緣</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">由</rdg></app>。一鬼問言。我常
<lb n="0560b16"/>苦頭痛。不知何罪所致。目連答言。汝本為人
<lb n="0560b17"/>時。不能修<note n="0560018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">忍＝善【三】【宮】</note><note n="0560018" resp="CBETA" type="mod">忍＝善【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0560018"><lem>忍</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">善</rdg></app>。以杖打眾生頭。今受花報果
<lb n="0560b18"/>在地獄。一鬼問言。我<note n="0560019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">常＋（患）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0560019" resp="CBETA" type="mod">常＋（患）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0560019"><lem>常</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">常患</rdg></app>瘡痛。何罪所致。<note n="0560020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（目連）＋答【三】【宮】</note><note n="0560020" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（目連）＋答【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0560020"><lem>答</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">目連答</rdg></app>
<lb n="0560b19"/>言。汝為人時。無有慈心。焚燒山<note n="0560021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">野＝林【三】【宮】</note><note n="0560021" resp="CBETA" type="mod">野＝林【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0560021"><lem>野</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">林</rdg></app>。殘害眾
<lb n="0560b20"/>生。今受花報果在地獄。一鬼問言。我舉身瘡
<lb n="0560b21"/>爛。<note n="0560022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">不可堪忍＝痛不可堪【三】【宮】</note><note n="0560022" resp="CBETA" type="mod">不可堪忍＝痛不可堪【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0560022"><lem>不可堪忍</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">痛不可堪</rdg></app>。何罪所致。答言。汝為人時。
<lb n="0560b22"/><note n="0560023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">喜燂＝生燖【三】【宮】</note><note n="0560023" resp="CBETA" type="mod">喜燂＝生燖【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0560023"><lem>喜燂</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">生燖</rdg></app>&CB00337;羊。今受花報果在地獄。一鬼問言。
<lb n="0560b23"/>我食<note n="0560024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">無足＝無有足時【三】【宮】</note><note n="0560024" resp="CBETA" type="mod">無足＝無有足時【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0560024"><lem>無足</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">無有足時</rdg></app>。初不得飽。何罪所致。答言。汝為
<lb n="0560b24"/>人時。<note n="0560025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">雖＝唯【宮】</note><app n="0560025"><lem>雖</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">唯</rdg></app><note n="0560026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">飯＋（食）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0560026" resp="CBETA" type="mod">飯＋（食）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0560026"><lem>飯</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">飯食</rdg></app>眾生。<note n="0560027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&M010527;令不＝初不令【三】【宮】</note><note n="0560027" resp="CBETA" type="mod">&M010527;令不＝初不令【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0560027"><lem>&M010527;令不</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">初不令</rdg></app>足。今受花報果
<lb n="0560b25"/>在地獄。一鬼問言。我<note n="0560028" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔常〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0560028" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔常〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0560028"><lem>常</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>苦頭痛。治之叵差。
<lb n="0560b26"/>何罪所致。答言。汝為人時。不敬道德。加以罵
<lb n="0560b27"/>辱。今受花報果在地獄。一鬼問言。我生男女。
<lb n="0560b28"/><note n="0560029" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">盡皆＝皆悉【三】【宮】</note><note n="0560029" resp="CBETA" type="mod">盡皆＝皆悉【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0560029"><lem>盡皆</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">皆悉</rdg></app>端正<note n="0560030" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔可愛〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0560030" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔可愛〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0560030"><lem>可愛</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>。而皆早死。念<note n="0560031" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">無＝之【三】【宮】</note><note n="0560031" resp="CBETA" type="mod">無＝之【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0560031"><lem>無</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">之</rdg></app>斷絕。何
<lb n="0560b29"/>罪所致。答言。汝為人時。見<note n="0560032" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">兒＝人【宮】</note><app n="0560032"><lem>兒</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">人</rdg></app>殺生。<note n="0560033" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">助喜噉＝助其歡喜共噉其【三】【宮】</note><note n="0560033" resp="CBETA" type="mod">助喜噉＝助其歡喜共噉其【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0560033"><lem>助喜噉</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">助其歡喜共噉其</rdg></app>
<pb ed="T" id="T17.0746.0560c" n="0560c"/>
<lb n="0560c01"/>肉。殺故<note n="0560034" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">促＝短【三】【宮】</note><note n="0560034" resp="CBETA" type="mod">促＝短【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0560034"><lem>促</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">短</rdg></app>命。喜故痛毒。今受花報果在地
<lb n="0560c02"/>獄。一鬼問言。我有一夫。而畜多婦。我應直
<lb n="0560c03"/>宿。而不見納。何罪所致。答言。汝為人時。不
<lb n="0560c04"/>敬夫主。邪婬無禮。今受花報果在地獄。一鬼
<lb n="0560c05"/>問言。我常頭痛。而男根瘡爛。何罪所致。答
<lb n="0560c06"/>言。汝為人時。於塔廟清淨之處行婬。今受花
<lb n="0560c07"/>報果在地獄。一鬼問言。我得此身。&CB00308;&CB00612;不淨。
<lb n="0560c08"/>何罪所致。答言。汝為人時。不尊有德。輕賤善
<lb n="0560c09"/>人。而以沙土。<note n="0560035" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">擲＝&CB13551;【三】</note><note n="0560035" resp="CBETA" type="mod">擲＝&CB13551;【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0560035"><lem>擲</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">&CB13551;</rdg></app>坌沙門。今受花報果在地
<lb n="0560c10"/>獄。一鬼問言。我食不啻一斛。而常不足。何罪
<lb n="0560c11"/>所致。答言。汝為人時。本作比丘。為僧求物。
<lb n="0560c12"/>而以自食。今受花報果在地獄。一鬼問言。我
<lb n="0560c13"/>受此形。&CB00560;腫項癭。何罪所致。答言。汝為人
<lb n="0560c14"/>時。使人及諸畜生。負重無道。今受花報果在
<lb n="0560c15"/>地獄。一鬼問言。我受此身。常患熱渴。何罪所
<lb n="0560c16"/>致。答言。汝為人時。喜好<note n="0560036" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">漁獵＝獵魚【宋】，魚獵【宮】</note><note n="0560036" resp="CBETA" type="mod">漁獵＝獵魚【宋】，＝魚獵【宮】</note><app n="0560036"><lem>漁獵</lem><rdg wit="【宋】" resp="Taisho">獵魚</rdg><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">魚獵</rdg></app>。以所得魚。投
<lb n="0560c17"/>之沙土。令其苦死。今受花報果在地獄。一鬼
<lb n="0560c18"/>問言。我受此身。<note n="0560037" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">狂癡＝癡狂【三】，常癡【宮】</note><note n="0560037" resp="CBETA" type="mod">狂癡＝癡狂【宋】【元】【明】，＝常癡【宮】</note><app n="0560037"><lem>狂癡</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">癡狂</rdg><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">常癡</rdg></app><note n="0560038" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">無＝不【宋】</note><app n="0560038"><lem>無</lem><rdg wit="【宋】" resp="Taisho">不</rdg></app><note n="0560039" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">智＝知【三】【宮】</note><note n="0560039" resp="CBETA" type="mod">智＝知【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0560039"><lem>智</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">知</rdg></app>。何罪所致。答
<lb n="0560c19"/>言。汝為人時。以酒施人。今受花報果在地獄。
<lb n="0560c20"/>一鬼問言。我所生子。皆反噉我。何罪所致。答
<lb n="0560c21"/>言。汝為人時。不修孝養。今受花報果在地獄。
<lb n="0560c22"/>一鬼問言。我食常吐。何罪所致。答言。汝為人
<lb n="0560c23"/>時。有人中後索<note n="0560040" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">食＋（者）【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0560040"><lem>食</lem><rdg wit="【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">食者</rdg></app>。<note n="0560041" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔汝〕－【宋】</note><app n="0560041"><lem>汝</lem><rdg wit="【宋】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>瞋<note n="0560042" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">罵＝詈【三】【宮】</note><note n="0560042" resp="CBETA" type="mod">罵＝詈【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0560042"><lem>罵</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">詈</rdg></app>而與。今受花
<lb n="0560c24"/>報果在地獄。一鬼問言。我今一生資財無乏。
<lb n="0560c25"/>而樂著弊<note n="0560043" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">衣＝故【三】</note><note n="0560043" resp="CBETA" type="mod">衣＝故【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0560043"><lem>衣</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">故</rdg></app>。何罪所致。答言。汝為人時。雖
<pb ed="T" id="T17.0746.0561a" n="0561a"/>
<lb n="0561a01"/>好布施。施後尋悔。今受花報果在地獄。一鬼
<lb n="0561a02"/>問言。我<note n="0561001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">受＝今【三】【宮】</note><note n="0561001" resp="CBETA" type="mod">受＝今【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0561001"><lem>受</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">今</rdg></app>一形。&M010527;倚巷陌。宿無常處。何罪
<lb n="0561a03"/>所致。答言。汝為人時。客來投止。而不安隱。
<lb n="0561a04"/>見他<note n="0561002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">容＝客【三】【宮】</note><note n="0561002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">容＝客【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0561002"><lem>容</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">客</rdg></app>止。而復瞋罵。今受華報果在地獄。
<lb n="0561a05"/>一鬼問言。我得此形。非男非女。何罪所致。答
<lb n="0561a06"/>言。汝為人時。而無慈心。好犍六畜。今受花報
<lb n="0561a07"/>果在地獄。一鬼問言。我得此身。<note n="0561003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">躄＝癖【宋】</note><app n="0561003"><lem>躄</lem><rdg wit="【宋】" resp="Taisho">癖</rdg></app>不能行。
<lb n="0561a08"/>何罪所致。答言。汝為人時<note n="0561004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">好行＝自好【宮】</note><app n="0561004"><lem>好行</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">自好</rdg></app>無道。拘繫
<lb n="0561a09"/><note n="0561005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">人獸＝於人及以禽獸【三】，於人多畜禽獸【宮】</note><note n="0561005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">人獸＝於人及以禽獸【宋】【元】【明】，＝於人多畜禽獸【宮】</note><app n="0561005"><lem>人獸</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">於人及以禽獸</rdg><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">於人多畜禽獸</rdg></app>。令不得行今受花報果在地獄。一鬼問
<lb n="0561a10"/>言。我此一身常患熱渴。行見&M010527;河。清涼<note n="0561006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">美＝甚【三】【宮】</note><note n="0561006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">美＝甚【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0561006"><lem>美</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">甚</rdg></app>
<lb n="0561a11"/>好。入中<note n="0561007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">洗＝洒【三】【宮】下同</note><note n="0561007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">洗＝洒【宋】【元】【明】【宮】下同</note><app n="0561007"><lem>洗</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">洒</rdg></app>浴。冀得涼樂。以除熱苦。方入其
<lb n="0561a12"/>中。舉身爛壞。渴欲飲之。一口入咽。五藏焦
<lb n="0561a13"/>爛。<note n="0561008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">飢＝肌【三】【宮】</note><note n="0561008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">飢＝肌【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0561008"><lem>飢</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">肌</rdg></app>肉離骨。何罪所致。答言。汝為人時。好
<lb n="0561a14"/>為相師。相人吉凶。少實多虛。或毀或譽。自稱
<lb n="0561a15"/>有德。以動人心。以求利養。又於父母兄弟宗
<lb n="0561a16"/>親。諂偽不實。今受花報果在地獄。<note n="0561009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">受苦億倍＝憂苦叵言【三】【宮】</note><note n="0561009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">受苦億倍＝憂苦叵言【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0561009"><lem>受苦億
<lb n="0561a17"/>倍</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">憂苦叵言</rdg></app>。說不可<note n="0561010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">盡＋（也）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0561010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">盡＋（也）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0561010"><lem>盡</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">盡也</rdg></app>。一鬼問言。我受身<note n="0561011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">以＝已【三】【宮】</note><note n="0561011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">以＝已【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0561011"><lem>以</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">已</rdg></app>來常有
<lb n="0561a18"/><note n="0561012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">惡＝一【三】【宮】</note><note n="0561012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">惡＝一【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0561012"><lem>惡</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">一</rdg></app>狗。體大牙利。兩目赫赤晝夜常來而噉我
<lb n="0561a19"/>身。命未盡頃肉<note n="0561013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">尋＝便【三】【宮】</note><note n="0561013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">尋＝便【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0561013"><lem>尋</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">便</rdg></app>復生。<note n="0561014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">復＝生【宮】</note><app n="0561014"><lem>復</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">生</rdg></app>受此苦。痛不可
<lb n="0561a20"/><note n="0561015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（堪）＋忍【三】【宮】</note><note n="0561015" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（堪）＋忍【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0561015"><lem>忍</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">堪忍</rdg></app>。何罪所致。答言。汝為人時。作天<note n="0561016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">祠＝祀【宋】【元】【宮】＊</note><app n="0561016"><lem>祠</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【宮】" resp="Taisho">祀</rdg></app>主。
<lb n="0561a21"/>於天<app type="＊" source="0561016"><lem>祠</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【宮】">祀</rdg></app>中。取牛羊血。以祀於天。自食其肉。
<lb n="0561a22"/>語眾人言。汝等<note n="0561017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">祀天＝祠祀【三】【宮】</note><note n="0561017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">祀天＝祠祀【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0561017"><lem>祀天</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">祠祀</rdg></app>。大得吉利。作<note n="0561018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">諸惡邪＝惡邪罪【三】【宮】</note><note n="0561018" resp="CBETA" type="mod">諸惡邪＝惡邪罪【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0561018"><lem>諸惡邪</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">惡邪罪</rdg></app>。
<lb n="0561a23"/>以惑百姓。今受花報果在地獄。一鬼問言。我
<lb n="0561a24"/>受此身。常<note n="0561019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">在＝處【三】【宮】</note><note n="0561019" resp="CBETA" type="mod">在＝處【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0561019"><lem>在</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">處</rdg></app>不淨<note n="0561020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔中〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0561020" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔中〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0561020"><lem>中</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>。舉身塗漫。有所噉食。
<lb n="0561a25"/>皆是不淨。&M010527;受此苦。不能得離。臭惱纏身。憂
<lb n="0561a26"/>患叵計。何罪所致。答言。汝為人時。作婆羅
<lb n="0561a27"/>門。不信佛法。不樂供養沙門道人。<note n="0561021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">若＝客【三】</note><note n="0561021" resp="CBETA" type="mod">若＝客【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0561021"><lem>若</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">客</rdg></app>來乞
<lb n="0561a28"/>求。&M010527;不欲見。時有一道人來從汝乞。汝作是
<lb n="0561a29"/>念。當作方便令不復來。即取&CB00425;盛屎著下。以
<pb ed="T" id="T17.0746.0561b" n="0561b"/>
<lb n="0561b01"/>飯覆上。<note n="0561022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">將＝持【三】【宮】</note><note n="0561022" resp="CBETA" type="mod">將＝持【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0561022"><lem>將</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">持</rdg></app>與道人。<note n="0561023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔道人〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0561023" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔道人〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0561023"><lem>道人</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>得已。還至本處。持
<lb n="0561b02"/>著一面。淨洗手訖。坐而執&CB00425;。<note n="0561024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">手取欲食＝取飯食之【三】【宮】</note><note n="0561024" resp="CBETA" type="mod">手取欲食＝取飯食之【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0561024"><lem>手取欲食</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">取飯食之</rdg></app>。&CB00425;
<lb n="0561b03"/>中不淨。臭不可近。以是因緣。受此臭惱。今受
<lb n="0561b04"/>花報果在地獄。<note n="0561025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">常＝當【三】【宮】</note><note n="0561025" resp="CBETA" type="mod">常＝當【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0561025"><lem>常</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">當</rdg></app>吞<note n="0561026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔熱〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0561026" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔熱〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0561026"><lem>熱</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>鐵丸。身體爛壞。苦
<lb n="0561b05"/>不可言。一鬼問言。我受此身。處處舌出。有自
<lb n="0561b06"/>然斧。而斬截之。如是無數。何罪所致。答言。
<lb n="0561b07"/>汝為人時。作小道人。為僧所差。取<note n="0561027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">冷＝清【三】【宮】</note><note n="0561027" resp="CBETA" type="mod">冷＝清【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0561027"><lem>冷</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">清</rdg></app>淨水。
<lb n="0561b08"/>作石蜜漿。分與眾僧。石蜜堅大。打取少<note n="0561028" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">許＋（而）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0561028" resp="CBETA" type="mod">許＋（而）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0561028"><lem>許</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">許而</rdg></app>。
<lb n="0561b09"/>盜<note n="0561029" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">食＋（之）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0561029" resp="CBETA" type="mod">食＋（之）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0561029"><lem>食</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">食之</rdg></app>一口。盜僧物故。今受華報果在地獄。
<lb n="0561b10"/>吞<note n="0561030" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">注＝於【三】【宮】</note><note n="0561030" resp="CBETA" type="mod">注＝於【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0561030"><lem>注</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">於</rdg></app>洋銅。苦不可<note n="0561031" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">言＝說【三】【宮】</note><note n="0561031" resp="CBETA" type="mod">言＝說【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0561031"><lem>言</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">說</rdg></app>。一鬼問言。我受此身。
<lb n="0561b11"/>常苦飢餓。往至廁上。欲取屎食。廁上有大力
<lb n="0561b12"/>鬼。以杖打我。初不得近。何罪所致。答言。汝
<lb n="0561b13"/>為人時。曾作道人。為佛圖主。&CB00385;護僧物。不以
<lb n="0561b14"/>好食供養眾僧。常以&CB00308;惡與之。或時<note n="0561032" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔時〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0561032" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔時〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0561032"><lem>時</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>欲作
<lb n="0561b15"/>好食。<note n="0561033" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（見）＋客【三】【宮】</note><note n="0561033" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（見）＋客【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0561033"><lem>客</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">見客</rdg></app>比丘來。便止不作。待去乃設。惡心
<lb n="0561b16"/>慳惜。今受花報果在地獄。<note n="0561034" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔一鬼…地獄〕六十七字－【宮】</note><app n="0561034" word-count="67"><lem>一鬼問言。我受
<lb n="0561b17"/>此身。腹大如甕。餘身分皆小。咽如<note n="0561035" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔細〕－【三】</note><note n="0561035" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔細〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0561035"><lem>細</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>針孔。
<lb n="0561b18"/>不得下食。何罪所致。答言。汝為人時。作聚落
<lb n="0561b19"/>主。自恃豪強。<note n="0561036" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">欺＋（凌）【三】</note><note n="0561036" resp="CBETA" type="mod">欺＋（凌）【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0561036"><lem>欺</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">欺凌</rdg></app>人民。常以無道。索人飲食。
<lb n="0561b20"/>以苦百姓。今受花報果在地獄</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>。一鬼問言。我
<lb n="0561b21"/>受此身。肩上有銅瓶。滿中洋銅。手捉一杓。以
<lb n="0561b22"/>酌取之。自灌其頭。舉身焦爛。如是無數。苦痛
<lb n="0561b23"/>無量。何罪所致。答言。汝為人時。出家修道。
<lb n="0561b24"/>知僧飲食。<note n="0561037" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">以＝取【三】【宮】</note><note n="0561037" resp="CBETA" type="mod">以＝取【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0561037"><lem>以</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">取</rdg></app>一酥瓶。藏著餘處。客道人來
<lb n="0561b25"/>而不與之。客去出<note n="0561038" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">酥＋（瓶）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0561038" resp="CBETA" type="mod">酥＋（瓶）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0561038"><lem>酥</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">酥瓶</rdg></app>行與舊僧。此酥是招
<lb n="0561b26"/>提僧物。一切有分。<note n="0561039" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（以）＋隱【三】【宮】</note><note n="0561039" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（以）＋隱【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0561039"><lem>隱</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">以隱</rdg></app>匿僧物。與不平等。以
<lb n="0561b27"/>是因緣。得如是苦。今受花報果在地獄。<note n="0561040" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">受苦＝苦痛【三】【宮】</note><note n="0561040" resp="CBETA" type="mod">受苦＝苦痛【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0561040"><lem>受
<lb n="0561b28"/>苦</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">苦痛</rdg></app>難計。一鬼問言。我受此身。常有人來。持
<lb n="0561b29"/><note n="0561041" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔諸〕－【宮】</note><app n="0561041"><lem>諸</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>刀鋸。<note n="0561042" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">割剝＝剝刺【三】【宮】</note><note n="0561042" resp="CBETA" type="mod">割剝＝剝刺【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0561042"><lem>割剝</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">剝刺</rdg></app>我身。又破<note n="0561043" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">其＝我【三】【宮】</note><note n="0561043" resp="CBETA" type="mod">其＝我【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0561043"><lem>其</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">我</rdg></app>腹。出其五藏。
<pb ed="T" id="T17.0746.0561c" n="0561c"/>
<lb n="0561c01"/>肉盡筋斷。痛不可<note n="0561044" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">忍＋（受）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0561044" resp="CBETA" type="mod">忍＋（受）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0561044"><lem>忍</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">忍受</rdg></app>。須臾之間。肉生平復。
<lb n="0561c02"/>尋復來割。何罪所致。答言。汝為人時。作婆
<lb n="0561c03"/>羅門。不信正法。常生邪見。奉事天神。&M010527;以牛
<lb n="0561c04"/>羊禱<note n="0561045" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">祠＝祀【三】【宮】</note><note n="0561045" resp="CBETA" type="mod">祠＝祀【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0561045"><lem>祠</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">祀</rdg></app>。以是罪故。今<note n="0561046" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">受＋（此苦此是）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0561046" resp="CBETA" type="mod">受＋（此苦此是）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0561046"><lem>受</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">受此苦此是</rdg></app>花報果在地獄。一
<lb n="0561c05"/>鬼問言。我受此身。常有人來。持諸刀鋸。割剝
<lb n="0561c06"/>我身。又破其腹。出其五藏。肉盡筋斷。苦切叵
<lb n="0561c07"/>忍。須臾之間。肉生平復。尋復來割。何罪所
<lb n="0561c08"/>致。答言。汝為人時。常作魁膾主。知殺人無有
<lb n="0561c09"/>慈心。歎喜行之。有如是罪。<note n="0561047" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">故得此惡＝得此苦痛【三】【宮】</note><note n="0561047" resp="CBETA" type="mod">故得此惡＝得此苦痛【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0561047"><lem>故得此惡</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">得此苦痛</rdg></app>。今受
<lb n="0561c10"/>花報果在地獄。一鬼問言。我受此身。兩腋下
<lb n="0561c11"/>&M010527;有熱<note n="0561048" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">鐵＋（輪行時）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0561048" resp="CBETA" type="mod">鐵＋（輪行時）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0561048"><lem>鐵</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">鐵輪行時</rdg></app>輪轉。<note n="0561049" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">大＝火【三】【宮】</note><note n="0561049" resp="CBETA" type="mod">大＝火【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0561049"><lem>大</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">火</rdg></app>熱逼身兩<note n="0561050" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">腋＋（下）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0561050" resp="CBETA" type="mod">腋＋（下）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0561050"><lem>腋</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">腋下</rdg></app>焦爛。何罪
<lb n="0561c12"/>所致。答言。汝為人時。出家學道。與僧<note n="0561051" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔作〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0561051" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔作〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0561051"><lem>作</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>種
<lb n="0561c13"/>種餅。僧未下食。汝時貪心盜取僧餅。藏著腋
<lb n="0561c14"/>下屏處食之。以是因緣得如是苦。今受花報
<lb n="0561c15"/>果在地獄。受苦難量。一鬼問言。我受此身。常
<lb n="0561c16"/>有自然赤鐵丸。從空中下。入口至腹。或<note n="0561052" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔從〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0561052" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔從〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0561052"><lem>從</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>
<lb n="0561c17"/>左出右入。<note n="0561053" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔或從〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0561053" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔或從〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0561053"><lem>或從</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>右出左入。舉身焦爛。<note n="0561054" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔痛切〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0561054" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔痛切〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0561054"><lem>痛切</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>
<lb n="0561c18"/>無量。何罪所致。答言。汝為人時。出家為
<lb n="0561c19"/>沙彌。為僧煮菴羅果。僧中行之。至和上前。
<lb n="0561c20"/><note n="0561055" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔輒〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0561055" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔輒〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0561055"><lem>輒</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>長與七枚。以是因緣。<note n="0561056" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">得如是惡＝故得惡苦【三】【宮】</note><note n="0561056" resp="CBETA" type="mod">得如是惡＝故得惡苦【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0561056"><lem>得如是惡</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">故得惡苦</rdg></app>。今受華
<lb n="0561c21"/>報果在地獄。一鬼問言。我受此身。意欲行來。
<lb n="0561c22"/>發動迴還。猶如旋風。初不得前。愁惱悶苦。不
<lb n="0561c23"/>可稱計。何罪所致。答言。汝為人時。作卜問
<lb n="0561c24"/>師。詭誑他人。令心<note n="0561057" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">罔＝幻【三】【宮】</note><note n="0561057" resp="CBETA" type="mod">罔＝幻【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0561057"><lem>罔</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">幻</rdg></app>惑。或喜或怖。皆不真
<pb ed="T" id="T17.0746.0562a" n="0562a"/>
<lb n="0562a01"/>實。由此因緣。得如是惡。今受花報果在地獄。
<lb n="0562a02"/>一鬼問言。我受此身。內常有熱。猶懷湯火。復
<lb n="0562a03"/>來燒煮。苦痛萬端。何罪所致。答言。汝為人
<lb n="0562a04"/>時。作國王第一夫人。時王<note n="0562001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">貴＝偏【三】【宮】</note><note n="0562001" resp="CBETA" type="mod">貴＝偏【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0562001"><lem>貴</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">偏</rdg></app>敬小夫人。汝
<lb n="0562a05"/>常生嫉心。作惡方便。求欲殺之。伺其臥時。煮
<lb n="0562a06"/>酥令熱。注著腹上。其人得此苦痛無量。遂
<lb n="0562a07"/><note n="0562002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">便＝致【三】【宮】</note><note n="0562002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">便＝致【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0562002"><lem>便</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">致</rdg></app>命終。由是因緣。得如是苦。今受花報果
<lb n="0562a08"/>在地獄。一鬼問言。<note n="0562003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔言〕－【宋】【元】【宮】</note><app n="0562003"><lem>言</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>我受此身。性多恐怖。
<lb n="0562a09"/>常畏人來。收閉繫縛。<note n="0562004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">枷鎖＝加諸【三】【宮】</note><note n="0562004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">枷鎖＝加諸【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0562004"><lem>枷鎖</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">加諸</rdg></app>楚毒。初無歡心。
<lb n="0562a10"/>何罪所致。答言。汝為人時。好行邪婬。犯人婦
<lb n="0562a11"/>女。常畏發覺。心不自寧。今受花報果在地獄。
<lb n="0562a12"/>或臥鐵床或抱銅柱。如是之<note n="0562005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">苦＝罪【三】【宮】</note><note n="0562005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">苦＝罪【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0562005"><lem>苦</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">罪</rdg></app>。不可稱計。
<lb n="0562a13"/>一鬼問言。我受此身。自然熱鐵。而有籠網。纏
<lb n="0562a14"/>絡我身。燒熱焦爛。痛毒叵言。何罪所致。答
<lb n="0562a15"/>言。汝為人時。<note n="0562006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔常〕－【宮】</note><app n="0562006"><lem>常</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>持<note n="0562007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">罝＝罥【三】，置【宮】</note><note n="0562007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">罝＝罥【宋】【元】【明】，＝置【宮】</note><app n="0562007"><lem>罝</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">罥</rdg><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">置</rdg></app>網。殺諸魚獸。籠取飛
<lb n="0562a16"/>鳥。以是因緣。得如是苦切。今受花報果在地
<lb n="0562a17"/>獄。一鬼問言。我受此身。無有手足。如一&CB00556;
<lb n="0562a18"/>肉。在於曠野。狐狼虎豹。鵰鷲眾鳥。競來搏
<lb n="0562a19"/>撮。爭共食之。苦痛叵言。何罪所致。答言。汝
<lb n="0562a20"/>為人時。作惡方便。若己若他。妊<note n="0562008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">身＝娠【元】【明】</note><app n="0562008"><lem>身</lem><rdg wit="【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">娠</rdg></app>之時。即
<lb n="0562a21"/>便與藥。令胎消化。由是因緣。得如是苦。今受
<lb n="0562a22"/>花報果在地獄。又三鬼一時來問言。我受此
<lb n="0562a23"/>身。常有鐵釘。從空中下。釘我身上。入肌破
<lb n="0562a24"/>骨。痛毒徹髓。何罪所致。答言。汝為人時。一
<lb n="0562a25"/>人作馬師。一人作牛師。一人作象師。苟貪他
<lb n="0562a26"/>財。鍼刺無道。使受痛苦。而不除痛。由是因
<lb n="0562a27"/>緣。得如是苦。今受花報果在地獄。一鬼問言。
<lb n="0562a28"/>我受此身。無有頭首。眼耳鼻口。盡在胸前。何
<lb n="0562a29"/>罪所致。答言。汝為人時。若見殺人。與之捉
<pb ed="T" id="T17.0746.0562b" n="0562b"/>
<lb n="0562b01"/>頭。歡喜而挽。無有慈心。由是因緣。得如是
<lb n="0562b02"/>身。今受花報果在地獄。目連答諸鬼已。皆生
<lb n="0562b03"/>敬心。走前懺悔。目連見其歡喜。更為說法。諸
<lb n="0562b04"/>鬼聞已。皆大歡喜</p></div1>
<lb n="0562b05"/><juan fun="close" n="001"><jhead><title>餓鬼報應經</title></jhead></juan>
